        "metric": "BMW B57/B58 — Frequently Asked Questions",
        "value": "1. How much does a BMW B57 or B58 engine replacement cost?"
      },
      {
        "metric": "A reconditioned B57 (diesel) costs £5,000–£8,000, while the B58 (petrol) is £3,800–£6,000 supply only [BMW‑QUOTE], varying by sub‑variant and vehicle. Fitting adds £650–£1,300. Use our calculator for your specific model.",
